*
TITLE 2x2  prob fcst
*
XDEF 36 LINEAR -130 2
*
YDEF 19 LINEAR   20 2
*
ZDEF 1 LEVELS  1  1
*
TDEF 999 LINEAR dec1995 1yr
*
